          "text": "Retraction Notice: Chat With ChatGPT on Intelligent Vehicles: An IEEE TIV Perspective"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "0000000000000000",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "96becbbeb77fbf0b",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "Retraction Notice: A Secured Vehicle Brain: DAO-Based Collaborative Perception and Decision-Making Systems for Intelligent Vehicles in CPSS"
        },
        {
